subSubSection.paragraph:
We conducted our searches using equal weights for minimizing transformations. In order to examine the effect of the gap treatment in our results, and following De Laet’s development (2005), we also submitted our final tree to a round of tree­bisection and reconnection branch swapping (
TBR
) by using a weighting scheme of 2 for substitutions and morphological transformations, 3 for a gap opening, and 1 for a gap extension.
